comments: Westbrook (HOU) cleanly dislodges the ball from Robinson (NYK) as he defends the shot near the rim.
Westbrook (HOU) re-establishes himself back in bounds prior to making contact with the ball.
Tucker (HOU) makes contact to Harkless' (NYK) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Harden (HOU) and Randle (NYK) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Harkless (NYK) makes contact to Harden's (HOU) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) extends his arm as he releases from the contact with Harden (HOU).
Covington (HOU) avoids making contact with Randle's (NYK) arm as Randle rips his arms through Covington's space.
Covington (HOU) brings his arm down and makes contact to Randle's (NYK) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Harden (HOU) is already in Ntilikina's (NYK) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Harkless (NYK) is moving alongside Westbrook's (HOU) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Robinson (NYK) off ball as he is receiving the pass.
Covington (HOU) cleanly blocks Randle's (NYK) shot near the rim.
Harden (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Randle's (NYK) shot near the rim.
Harkless (NYK) is moving alongside Harden's (HOU) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive to the basket.
Barrett (NYK) legally contests Harden's (HOU) driving shot attempt.
Tucker (HOU) moves parallel alongside Barrett's (NYK) path to the basket and as they meet at a simultaneous point Barrett does not extend his arm to dislodge Tucker from his legal guarding position.
Tucker (HOU) legally contests Barrett's (NYK) driving shot attempt.
Ntilikina (NYK) reaches in and makes contact to Westbrook's (HOU) arm prior to making contact with the ball.
Harden (HOU) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
Ntilikina (NYK) is moving alongside Westbrook's (HOU) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive to the basket.
As Westbrook (HOU) attempts the cross over and connect with Ntlikina (NYK) he pins the ball against his body and then he continues to dribble.
Ntilikina (NYK) legally contests Westbrook's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
